
# Access Controls Worksheet

## Authorization/Authentication

### Objective: Notes to Identify the Threat
- The event took place on 10/03/23.
- The user is listed as Legal/Administrator.
- The IP address of the computer used to log in is 152.207.255.255.

### Objective: Authorization Issues Identified
- Robert Taylor Jr is not an admin.
- His contract ended in 2019, but his account accessed payroll systems in 2023.

### Objective: Recommendations to Prevent Future Incidents
- User accounts should expire after 30 days of inactivity.
- Contractors should have limited access to business resources.
- Enable Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA) to secure account access.

